{"tid":1033705,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋招募員] World of Tanks","createTime":"2019-02-23T11:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T12:27:29.000Z","uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85b42b11058624dc4fdec1e292e2cc9f645fe244","tid":1033705,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:23:10.000Z","msg":"推薦計畫 2.0<br />\n任何一位在遊戲中進行過 1,000 場或以上隨機戰鬥的玩家，都能夠成為招募員並且邀請學員。  <br />\n<br />\n如果滿足下列任一條件，您就可以應徵招募員的招募成爲學員：<br />\n<br />\n== 您是《戰車世界》的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新手</span></strong>，或參與過的戰鬥為<strong> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">200 場或以下</span> </strong>==<br />\n== 您在過去<strong> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">60 天內</span></strong>都未進行過遊戲 ==<br />\n<br />\n《戰車世界》推薦計畫 2.0 將由<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連續三個階段</span></strong>所組成。想要完成各個階段，招募員和學員必須完成隨機戰鬥的特殊任務來獲得一定數量的<strong>推薦點數</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n招募員和學員都有機會獲得大量獎勵，包含：<br />\n<br />\n= 點券<br />\n= 標誌<br />\n= 標語<br />\n= 迷彩<br />\n= 2D 風格<br />\n= 以及更多獎勵！<br />\n<br />\n更棒的還在後頭呢！<br />\n學員可從預定名單裡選擇一輛<strong> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">VI 階或 VII 階加值車輛</span></strong> (或選擇得到銀幣)。<br />\n招募員可挑選一輛<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> VIII 階加值戰車</span></strong> (或選擇得到銀幣)。<br />\n敬請留意即將發表的介紹推薦計畫 2.0 的專屬文章！"},{"pid":"be9e971e9eb226d35d467e647a44ab4253cd1cf9","tid":1033705,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"利申<br />\n您在過去 60 天內都未進行過遊戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932ea79206b288d5fadc9bb82e63091beba1eb21","tid":1033705,"uid":193193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"點玩架"},{"pid":"3edb7cbf8a1566600fac62216a9c4b38b03b56f4","tid":1033705,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"仲未收皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef9bfd93fe79a1ac8d1a7cc0fdad